Package: sitingclass
Type: Package
Title: Siting Classification of Norwegian Weather Stations
Version: 1.4.0
Author: Pierre-Marie Lefeuvre
Maintainer: Pierre-Marie Lefeuvre <pierre.marie.lefeuvre@met.no>
Description: `sitingclass` evaluates the exposure of weather stations for specific sensors from digital elevation models. The package is currently designed for Met usage only, due to data restrictions.
URL: https://gitlab.met.no/pierreml/sitingclass, https://pmlefeuvre-met.github.io/sitingclass/
